videos.description: Kolbe Caldwell drives to the basket and draws contact on the layup for a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Caldwell makes nice and-1 play for Utes

videos.description: Deandre Ayton gets a pass from Allonzo Trier and finishes with the slam to extend Arizona's lead.
videos.headline: Ayton throws down on Utes

videos.description: Justin Bibbins makes a 3-pointer and draws a foul on the play to cut Arizona's lead.
videos.headline: Utes work their way back with 4-point play

videos.description: Dusan Ristic finds Deandre Ayton under the basket and he finishes with a slam.
videos.headline: Ayton quiets Utah fans with dunk

videos.description: Sedrick Barefield creates a turnover and drains a 3-pointer on the other end to make it a 2-point game.
videos.headline: Utes create close game with steal and score

videos.description: Sedrick Barefield makes a 3-pointer to make it a one-point game and giving him 20 points in the second half vs. No. 14 Arizona.
videos.headline: Barefield stays hot from behind the arc for Utes
